metadata.name: GM #01
metadata.description:
Hi, I'm Nikxname. You can call me Nik! - I've been working as an artist for a couple of years and over that time I have created a variety of pieces exploring various themes and characters. My art features original characters designs which had no life outside of that work, until now.

The 'GM Art Collection' is meant to explore the fun, excitement and great energy a Good Morning can have, and I want everyone to get involved.

Each piece in the collection is a 1/1 work handcrafted by me.
